===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|fulminātus}}, past participle of {{m|la|fulminō||lighten, hurl or strike with lightning}}, from {{term|fulmen||lightning which strikes and sets on fire, thunderbolt|lang=la}}, from earlier {{m|la|*fulgmen}}, {{m|la|*fulgimen}}, from {{m|la|fulgō}}, {{m|la|fulgeō||flash, lighten}}. More at {{l|en|fulgent}}.

